AGI - A cycle link between the two Ferrari museums, Maranello and Modena's birthplace >, passing through Formigine and Fiorano, with a common sign that individuals the continuity of the track and the characters, also with the aim of enhancing it and promoting it for tourist purposes. It is the so-called 'Cyclovia del Mito' whose route of about 21 kilometers will be presented in the next days along with the brand.
&nbsp;
Meanwhile, the Municipality of Modena, unanimously approved the convention between the four municipalities and the Province for the realization of the works of characterization and signage, for a total cost of 50 thousand euros. The measure, illustrated by the Councillor for Mobility Alessandra Filippi, provides a cost of 10 thousand euros for each institution.
&nbsp;
The project of the 'Cyclovia del Mito' has already been presented in some events, such as the Misano Bike Fest>, raising the interest of the tourist operators. The initiative is developed by the Dmo (Destination management organization) of the Province of Modena in collaboration with Modenatur.
&nbsp;
Opening the debate, Francesca Fabbri (Pd) underlined the benefits of cycling paths, increasingly at the center of an expanding tourism: "They make economic induceds, knowledge of decentralized places and physical activity." For the councilwoman, therefore, it is right to upgrade its use and accessibility, also providing refreshment and repair points for bikes, "with the aim of extending the tourist season more and more".
&nbsp;
"It is a deliberation that repays us from the sorrows that we sometimes have as environmentalists," said Paola Aime (Green-Green Europe) reiterated that cycling tourism is an area that brings advantages in different areas, such as economics, but also to health and environment. The councilwoman, finally, has specified the importance of promoting along the points paths that allow the same cyclists to independently repair their means.
&nbsp;
Giovanni Bertoldi (Lega Modena) also affirmed the importance of supporting the diffusion of cycling tourism, proposing also to valorize other paths, such as the "moderate rhythm" of the cycle path EuroVelo 7: "On this issue we proposed, in 2020, a motion then approved: but little has been done and the Bologna route has become preeminent." &nbsp;
